    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "At the trades council meeting last\nnight four women delegates were\ntemporarily admitted and will later\nbe regularly seated as members. They\nwin represent the new telephone oper-\nators' union, which now has a mem\nbersbip of about 100.\n\n\nThe new delegates are Misses Ma\nbel Carter Lalla Barrett, Ethel Cof-\nfern and Edna Olmstead. There are\nother women delegates to the cohn-\nGil. but these are the first representa-\ntives this union has had."
    }
